author: rhuijben
msg: Following up on r1570022, remove the now unneeded wrapping of the diff
processor. This wrapping was already handled in diff_file_added(), and
this patch applies the same transform in diff_dir_added().
Removing this wrapping should allow future svn diff --git output
improvements in cases where we used to miss information.
diff_repos_wc): Remove setters of unused variables.
